column5: Awe come on dawg!  I was wondering the other night while watching the catfish noodleing championship if that was something that you are into
wonder what happens if he gets that long nose in the gut one time?  guess that means the fish wins?  Cheers!
sign me up ! looks like a BLAST
NOOOo wayyy Thats not the fish that i would jump on with that big spear as nose lol. Crazy tho
WOW, that is the best video i've seen in a while... hahahaha
funny how they spot it for the heli but the diver is already there filming,,lol
Good observation....  pretty outrageous, I also think we would have nearly broken his neck with the way he hit the water.
I can see his next adventure.  Jumping from above....then half way down thinking "That marlin sure looks like a great white shark.....awwww crap".
That would have been as much to make as it was to film it...  Freaken OUTRAGEOUS MAN!!  mass forward coming up.  HD
